name: Mod Style Tank Top
description: This is a really cute mod-looking tank top with a unique floral print. It is very comfortable and adorable, looks amazing paired with almost anything...a skirt, shorts, jeans etc. I usually wear a XS/S top and this M fits me pretty well (as seen in picture).

name: Floral Maxi Skirt
description: I am not sure what material this is because it does not say on the tag, but it is very light and airy! The floral pattern is very fun and perfect for warmer weather, especially if you are attending any outdoor concerts/ festivals!. Looks super cute flats, a hat, feathers/flowers in your hair. The tag says medium, but it seems to be a "bigger" medium. (I wear a small between 0-2 and it's big on me...I had to pin it in the back so that it would not fall down during the picture, haha).

name: Black blouse
description: This is a cute little black babydoll blouse. It's sleeves are a little puffed. Features a white color interlaces with a velvet like ribbon that ties into a bow and cute little red buttons up to the neck.

name: Floral Maxi Dress
description:
This is a gorgeous maxi dress, perfect for hot summer days. It is loose fitting therefore it flows beautifully. The floral print is very unique and consists of vibrant colors! It has an open back, and a low front. Definitely very playful, and it can be worn both casually and "dressy" depending on how you accessorize it.

Size: M. I usually wear a size small or x-small in dresses and this dress is the perfect length, it's just a little loose in the back.

Brand: Angela

Material is not listed, but I think it is some sort of Polyester, however it does not stick when you sweat.

I paid $45.00 for it.

name: LBD
description:
This is an ORIGINAL A.B.S. dress by Allen Schwartz. It is a size 12 black dress with gems and a halter neckline. Super cute and flirty for nights out. Value price around $375.
